aa(lp77
VHumanae is a pursuit to highlight our true colors,
p78
aVrather than the untrue
p79
aVwhite, red, black or yellow associated with race.
p80
aVIt's a kind of game to question our codes.
p81
aVIt's a work in progress from a personal story to a global history.
